# Keep the handoff / export / icons / texture docs under git. The
# repo-root `.gitignore` has `*.md` + `!docs/**/*.md`, but the
# un-ignore pattern is anchored to the repo root and does not
# propagate into nested crates. Re-enable it explicitly here.
!docs/handoff/*.md
!docs/export/*.md
!docs/icons/*.md
!docs/texture/*.md

# Bench harness transient output (worker stdout / GNU time / .pid / .ps).
# Keep raw/ JSONL + summaries/ JSON+MD as the persistent evidence.
reports/**/logs/

# Re-include summary markdowns under reports/ — the *.md ignore from the
# repo-root .gitignore would otherwise hide them, but they are part of the
# evidence chain referenced from README.md / NEXT.md.
!reports/**/*.md
